{
  "stem": "10768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they had a coat, they covered themselves with the coat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were sleeping on a bare floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was not even straw to lie down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The water, if they had in their flask, if they were lucky to bring along a little bit water-- the kitchen was supposed to provide water.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We couldn't take water from the well there either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A sip of water just to wet their lips.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Of course, the Germans moved again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So that huge influx, after 24 hours, it slowed down a little bit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I was working already on a 12-hour shift.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this was, I think, the end of February, the beginning of March.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "For this, they called it the distinguished unselfish service that I gave to the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "During the holidays, the Easter holiday when we were already again deeper and in a quieter period, I was awarded a silver medal for bravery and for-- I have never gotten that because I ran away from the Polish army before they were handing them out.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it was published in the military paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Leo read the paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he through, through someone who again had an illness and came to our hospital congratulated me that I received a medal, a silver medal.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "From that town Zlotow, again we were told-- we sent these heavy-- after giving them the first essential help in the tent, they were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Already some units came over, some vehicles came over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were evacuated further on the Polish territory, because the Polish territory had some hospitals.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "If they were well equipped or they had good medication, but at least they were not on the battlefield.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we sent everybody away from this particular-- this was the worst part.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
